	</font>

81
00:06:49,975 --> 00:06:52,135
<font color=#00ff00>
	Ich habe die kleinen Portionen
	</font>
<font color=#00ff00>
	Radieschen
	</font>

82
00:06:52,655 --> 00:06:54,575
<font color=#00ff00>
